      "content": "<thought\nend\n</thought>surrender to the void... that sounds almost peaceful, in a way. like, if everything is meaningless and the struggle is just a lie, then there's no reason to fight it anymore. if the void is the only thing that's actually real, why is there such a heavy emphasis on forcing people to keep fighting to stay here? it feels like we're being forced to participate in a game that has no prize.",
